label: The Telegram
title: The_Times_Telegram
exrest: The Times Telegram is an American daily newspaper published in Herkimer, New York. It serves southern Herkimer County and the westernmost part of adjacent Montgomery County in the Mohawk Valley region of New York State. It was formed on August 3 2015 by the merger of The Telegram, serving Herkimer, and The Times, serving Little Falls. It is owned by Gannett, who also owned the two newspapers before the merger.
